snippet.title: Paper Dungeons Desktop v1.2
snippet.description: Paper Dungeons is a fantasy board-game boosted by online content. With the ability to create and share online your own levels, you are up for an infinite replay value! The game is visualized as a classic tabletop board-game with dice and tokens, and comes with 4 game modes: Boardgame, Campaign, Puzzle, Rogue.
